OL,3,CManchester Arena attack survivors win
OL,4,CHigh Court harassment claim
OL,6,FA former television producer undertook
OL,7,F"a negligent, indeed reckless, abuse
OL,8,Fof media freedom" when he attempted to
OL,9,Fprove his belief the Manchester Arena
OL,10,Fbombing had been staged, a judge has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe comments came as two Manchester
OL,14,FArena bombing survivors won their High
OL,15,FCourt harassment case against Richard
OL,16,FHall, who followed the pair around
OL,17,Ffilming and photographing them.
