OL,3,CManchester Arena attack survivors win
OL,4,CHigh Court harassment claim
OL,6,FMartin Hibbert and his daughter Eve
OL,7,Fsued Hall for harassment and data
OL,8,Fprotection over his claims in several
OL,9,Fvideos and a book that the attack was
OL,10,Fstaged.
OL,12,FThe father and daughter suffered life-
OL,13,Fchanging injuries at the Ariana Grande
OL,14,Fconcert in May 2017, with Mr Hibbert
OL,15,Fleft with a spinal cord injury and
OL,16,FMiss Hibbert facing severe brain
OL,17,Fdamage.
