OL,6,FMr Hall, from Consett, County Durham,
OL,7,Fclaimed that the attack, in which
OL,8,FSalman Abedi detonated a home-made
OL,9,Frucksack bomb in the crowd of concert-
OL,10,Fgoers, was faked, and attempted to
OL,11,Fgather "evidence" to prove his point.
OL,13,FHe claimed his actions ` including an
OL,14,Fincident of filming Miss Hibbert
OL,15,Foutside her home ` were in the public
OL,16,Finterest as a journalist, and that
OL,17,F"millions of people have bought a lie"
OL,18,Fabout the attack.
