OL,3,CManchester Arena attack survivors win
OL,4,CHigh Court harassment claim
OL,6,FIn a 63-page judgment, on Wednesday,
OL,7,F23 October, Mrs Justice Steyn said the
OL,8,FHibberts had won their harassment
OL,9,Fclaim, but said she would not decide
OL,10,Fthe data protection claim at this
OL,11,Fstage.
OL,13,FThe judge described Mr Hall's actions
OL,14,Fas "a negligent, indeed reckless,
OL,15,Fabuse of media freedom" and said that
OL,16,Fthe trained engineer is "blinkered in
OL,17,Fhis belief that the false story he has
OL,18,Fspun is true".
OL,26,@vD@DOUwD@WO]xD@YOUzD@MO]
