OL,6,FMrs Justice Steyn added: "Over a
OL,7,Fperiod of years, he has repeatedly
OL,8,Fpublished false allegations, based on
OL,9,Fthe flimsiest of analytical
OL,10,Ftechniques, and dismissing the
OL,11,Fobvious, tragic reality to which so
OL,12,Fmany ordinary people have attested.
OL,14,F"He has published his allegations
OL,15,Fwidely, on a variety of platforms,
OL,16,Fover a period of years to viewers and
OL,17,Freaders in this jurisdiction likely
OL,18,Fnumbering well over 100,000.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUvD@AOU
