OL,6,F"He has done so for commercial gain,
OL,7,Falbeit I accept his evidence that the
OL,8,Ffinancial benefit to him has only been
OL,9,Fsufficient to enable him to continue
OL,10,Fhis work.
OL,12,F"All of this conduct has a natural
OL,13,Ftendency to cause serious distress,
OL,14,Fespecially when those targeted are
OL,15,Fvulnerable."
