OL,6,FSalman Abedi killed 22 people and
OL,7,Finjured hundreds when he detonated the
OL,8,Fhomemade rucksack-bomb in the crowd of
OL,9,Fconcert-goers, with the court told
OL,10,Fthat the Hibberts were among those
OL,11,Fstanding nearest to him at the time of
OL,12,Fthe blast.
OL,14,FThe judge said in her ruling that by
OL,15,Fthe time Mr Hall published his book
OL,16,Fand some of the videos, the suicide-
OL,17,Fbomber's brother Hashem Abedi had been
OL,18,Fconvicted, "yet Mr Hall paid no heed
OL,19,Fto the facts that demonstrated the
OL,20,Fjury found proved to the criminal
OL,21,Fstandard".
