OL,6,FMrs Justice Steyn continued: "Mr Hall
OL,7,Fhas published and continues to publish
OL,8,Fhis false allegations despite the
OL,9,Fattack having been the subject of
OL,10,Fthorough investigations, a criminal
OL,11,Ftrial, and authoritative reports which
OL,12,Fany reasonable person would recognise
OL,13,Fcommand respect.
OL,15,F"Mr Hall's publications are not only
OL,16,Ffalse, but they also lack any
OL,17,Fsemblance of balance."
