OL,6,FShe added: "Mr Hall knew that Mr
OL,7,FHibbert said his teenage daughter, who
OL,8,Fhe had taken to the concert, had been
OL,9,Fhit in the head by a bolt propelled by
OL,10,Fthe explosion, and that she had been
OL,11,Fvery severely injured.
OL,13,F"He also knew that her family were
OL,14,Fshielding her from any media attention.
