OL,6,F"From the available information, it
OL,7,Fshould have been readily apparent to
OL,8,Fany journalist ` even if the
OL,9,Findividual journalist was highly
OL,10,Fsceptical of the 'official narrative'
OL,11,F` that Eve should be treated as a
OL,12,Fvulnerable young person who had been
OL,13,Fcaught up and severely injured in a
OL,14,Ftraumatic incident."
OL,16,FMartin Hibbert described the decision
OL,17,Fas a "comprehensive victory", adding:
OL,18,F"I am really pleased with not only the
OL,19,Foverall judgment, but also the many
OL,20,Fcomments of the judge as to how
OL,21,Funacceptable Hall's behaviour was."
