OL,6,FHe said that he was hoping for an
OL,7,Finjunction, adding: "I do want this to
OL,8,Fopen the door for change, and to help
OL,9,Fprotect others from what we have been
OL,10,Fput through in the future.
OL,12,F"I will be discussing this with my
OL,13,Flegal team at Hudgell Solicitors, with
OL,14,Fthe aim of establishing a new law in
OL,15,FEve's name."
OL,17,FThe data protection claim, as well as
OL,18,Fany damages or injunctions, will be
OL,19,Fdecided at a later date.
